Changes to Clock
================

24-Mar-2006
~~~~~~~~~~~
Added es translation (Juan Carlos Jimenez Garcia).

18-Mar-2006 (2.1.7)
~~~~~~~~~~~
Cast strings passed to/from libxml to avoid compiler warnings.

05-Jan-2006
~~~~~~~~~~~
Fix problem with drawing alarm symbol far too small when panel initializing.

30-Dec-2005
~~~~~~~~~~~
Added i18n support.
Remove deprecated call.

24-Oct-2005
~~~~~~~~~~~
Added Zero Install injector feed.

12-Oct-2005 (2.1.6)
~~~~~~~~~~~
Update for ROX-CLib changes, many externally visible symbols
(functions and types) now have rox_ or ROX prefixes.
Alarms are show in the system tray.
Can get ROX-CLib via 0launch.

11-Sep-2005
~~~~~~~~~~~
Remove aclocal.m4, replace with rox-clib.m4 and aclocal -I .

27-Jul-2005
~~~~~~~~~~~
Made alarm windows sticky.

27-May-2005
~~~~~~~~~~~
Fix for creating applets in remote mode, need to give the filer long enough
to notice the widget was created.
Use apsymbols for Linux portability.

07-May-2005 (2.1.5)
~~~~~~~~~~~
Faster creation of small face displays.

04-Mar-2005
~~~~~~~~~~~
Fix bug creating alarm window.

29-Oct-2004 (2.1.4)
~~~~~~~~~~~
Switch to rox_info_win.

23-Oct-2004
~~~~~~~~~~~
Window counting now handled by ROX-CLib.  Use new rox_choices_load/save() 
interface.

07-Oct-2004
~~~~~~~~~~~
Use $MAKE instead of make when building.

27-Sep-2004
~~~~~~~~~~~
Set name on digital readout widget so it can be themed.

2.1.3
-----
React to change of font. Icon to indicate if alarms are set.

2.1.2
-----
alarm.c would not compile with virgin ROX-CLib.

2.1.1
-----
Draw clock face at higher resolution.
Less flicker when clock face bigger.
Numbers on clock face scale with face size.
Change to new libdir compilation system.
Changed some deprecated GTK+ functions.

2.1.0
-----
Get rid of some legacy code. 
Use ROX-CLib 2.1.0, including aclocal.m4.
Stock icons in the menu.
Open options dialog from command line.

2.0.0
-----
Stable release to go with ROX-CLib 2.0.0.

1.5.2
-----
Italian translation of AppInfo provided by Yuri Bongiorno.
Safer way to parse ROX-CLib's version number by Christopher Arndt.

1.5.1
-----
Conversion to new options system, switched to Pango fonts.
New option to not show clock face (requested by Klaus Umbach).

1.5.0
-----
New version for GTK+ 2.0 and ROX-CLib 1.1.0

1.4.1
-----
Fix for being installed in paths with spaces in.

1.4.0
-----
Stable version (unchanged from 1.3.3).

1.3.3
-----
Fix compilation with libxml2.

1.3.2
-----
Use replacement applet menu positioning code (from ROX-CLib).

1.3.1
-----
Another attempt at fixing the bug when time zone changes.c

1.3.0
-----
Multiple windows.  Acts as a server, using SOAP, so there only needs to be
one instance running.

1.2.1
-----
Make sure AppRun can find rox_run.

1.2.0
-----
Minor fixes.

1.1.8
-----
Fix compilation problems.

1.1.7
-----
Use new applet menu positioning code.

1.1.6
-----
Use font selection dialog instead of widget.
Added a monday-thursday repeat.
Test for altzone in <time.h>

1.1.5
-----
Change to XML handling: requires 2.4 or later.  Use old style config otherwise.

1.1.4
-----
Fix memory leak in XML routines.

1.1.3
-----
Can set font for the hour numbers.
Can use a tiled background if you set up your gtkrc.
Fixed bug in new XML format (interval was incorrect)

1.1.2
-----
Configuration and alarms now saved in XML format, old format still supported
when reading.

1.1.1
-----
Small changes to compilation system.

1.1.0
-----
Switch to using ROX-CLib.

1.0.0
-----
No changes.  This is the stable version.

0.1.15
------
Fixed bug in memory management.

0.1.14
------
Support menu accelerators.  Fix bugs in merging alarm files.

0.1.13
------
Drop old (0.1.6) config sypport.  Save alarms file after one is raised.

0.1.12
------
Can configure the initial size

0.1.11
------
Fixed bug in repeating alarms.

0.1.10
------
Fixed bug concealing text label.  Fixed bug in update code.
Some clock face display tweaks.

0.1.9
-----
Added repeating alarms.
Can have the menu on the applet version.

0.1.8
-----
Rudimentary alarm facility.

0.1.7
-----
Support new AppInfo.xml data, debug output off by default.

0.1.6
-----
Re-organised the configuration of the app.  Some tweaks to the display.

0.1.5
-----
Added some locale handling.

0.1.4
-----
More display styles, including a user defined one.

0.1.3
-----
Added different display styles, and a configuration window to choose one.

0.1.2
-----
Corrected hour hand.

0.1.1
-----
Added info window
